(122, 2, '2015-06-12 13:26:59', '2015-06-12 13:26:59', '<p>The Mykrobe predictor is designed for use by microbiologists and doctors, providing information needed in order to choose the best treatment. It analyses the whole genome of a bacterial sample, all within a couple of minutes, and predicts which drugs the infection is resistant to. No expertise is needed to run or interpret it, and it works on a standard desktop or laptop.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>FAQs</h2>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><b><strong>What species does Mykrobe support? </strong></b>\r\n<p>Currently we support sequence data that is expected to be from S. aureus or M. tuberculosis.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li> <b> <strong>Is there a version I can use that\'s not on basespace? </strong></b>\r\n<p> Yes, please visit <a href=\"http://www.mykrobe.com/products/predictor/\">http://www.mykrobe.com/products/predictor/</a> </p></li>\r\n<li><b><strong>I want to report a bug</strong></b>\r\n<p>Thanks! Please visit <a href=\"https://github.com/iqbal-lab/Mykrobe-predictor/issues/new\" target=\"_blank\">our issue tracker</a></p> </li>\r\n</ul>', 'Basespace FAQ', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '119-autosave-v1', '', '', '2015-06-12 13:26:59', '2015-06-12 13:26:59', '', 119, 'http://www.mykrobe.com/2015/06/12/119-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
